Geant4 Simulation for Radon Emanation
=====================================

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Primary Authors: Mayur Aitavadekar, Dr. Xiaochun He
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

# usage:
--------

1) clone from test-branch (all updated code is on test-branch)

> git clone -b test-branch https://github.com/phyxch/neutronBall.git 


# commands:
-----------

after running code in interactive mode, you can optionally use following
commands for better visibility and understanding of detector geometry.

* /vis/viewer/set/style surface OR wireframe
* /vis/viewer/addCutawayPlane 0 1 0 
* /vis/viewer/set/background white

# Instructions to run simulation
--------------------------------

* build code using cmake and make

1) run code interative mode:

> ./neutronBall
> /control/execute u238c.mac

2) run code in batch mode

> ./neutronBall ../neutronBall/macros/u238c.mac

# Results
---------

1) output.root file stores various results.
2) need to develop histograms (work in progress)
3) need to get good plots using output.root file (work in progress)

    
